#: ../../hardware/controllers/electrix_tweaker.md:17
msgid "Compatibility and setup"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/electrix_tweaker.md:20
msgid ""
"The Tweaker is a USB MIDI class compliant device, so it does not require any"
" special drivers on any operating system. Just plug it in and load the Mixxx"
" mapping on any OS that Mixxx runs on."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/electrix_tweaker.md:24
msgid ""
"Use it with the Tweaker MIDI 1 port (Tweaker MIDI 2 is the 5-pin MIDI I/O on"
" the Tweaker)."
msgstr ""

