msgid "Play/pause"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/electrix_tweaker.md:120
msgid ""
"Hotcues. Press an unlit button to set a hotcue. When slip mode is disabled "
"(see #9 below), pressing a hotcue simply jumps to that hotcue. When slip "
"mode is on, hotcues can be previewed on a stopped deck. While previewing a "
"hotcue, press the play button to let the track keep playing after the hotcue"
" is released. Pressing a hotcue while a deck is playing and slip mode is on "
"will jump to the hotcue then jump back to where the track would have been "
"once the last hotcue button is released."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/electrix_tweaker.md:128
msgid "Jump 4 beats forward (with quantize enabled)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/electrix_tweaker.md:129
msgid ""
"Slip mode. When active, loops and hotcues will only play as long as they are"
" held down. When they are released, the track will jump to where it would "
"have been if the loop or hotcue was not pressed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/electrix_tweaker.md:132
msgid "[[#deck-shift-layer|Deck shift]]"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/electrix_tweaker.md:133
msgid ""
"Deck toggle between decks 1 & 3 on the left and decks 2 & 4 on the right."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/electrix_tweaker.md:134
msgid "Jump 4 beats backward (with quantize enabled)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/electrix_tweaker.md:135
msgid ""
"Quantize. In addition to snapping cues, loops, and play button presses to "
"the nearest beat, this changes the behavior of the controller’s navigation "
"buttons. When enabled, the navigation buttons are white as shown by 8 & 11 "
"in the diagram. With quantize enabled, the navigation buttons jump by 4 "
"beats or 1 beat with [[#deck-shift-layer|deck shift (#10)]] pressed. When "
"disabled, the navigation buttons are green as shown by 15 & 16 in the "
"diagram. With quantize disabled, the navigation buttons fast forward and "
"rewind the track. When quantize is disabled and deck shift is pressed, the "
"navigation buttons are temporary pitch bend buttons."
msgstr ""

