msgid "Electrix Tweaker (vinyl timecode mode)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/electrix_tweaker.md:241
msgid "Top Shift"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/electrix_tweaker.md:242
msgid ""
"Toggle vinyl timecode mode by pressing deck shift (#2 in the diagram) while "
"holding top shift (#1 in the the diagram). This replaces the navigation "
"buttons for that deck with buttons that toggle options for timecode control."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/electrix_tweaker.md:243
msgid ""
"Cycle through vinyl control modes: absolute (LED off), relative (LED "
"indicates cue mode), and constant (LED red). If the deck is in relative mode"
" and playing, pressing the button cycles through cue modes: off (white), cue"
" (yellow), hotcue (green). When the deck is playing in relative mode, "
"pressing the button with deck shift (#2) switches to constant mode."
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/electrix_tweaker.md:244
msgid ""
"toggle vinyl control. Turns green when vinyl control is enabled. With deck "
"shift (#2) pressed, it toggles passthrough mode and turns white.  Pressing "
"the button while passthrough mode is enabled turns passthrough mode off "
"(without toggling whether vinyl control is enabled)."
msgstr ""
